"This string array stores the history of searches for hex values within the "
"internal file viewer."
msgstr ""
"Ce tableau conserve l’historique des recherches de valeurs hexadécimales "
"dans le visionneur interne."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1083
